<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٣٤ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَخْرَجَهُ:</span> مِنْ حَدِيثِ اِبْنِ عَبَّاسٍ بِلَفْظٍ: نَهَى.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَزَادَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«وَكُلُّ ذِي مِخْلَبٍ مِنَ الطَّيْرِ»</span>. <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
